6", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75348040_172907272437109_6662049577199960309_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=5WZ1ffAItxIQ7kNvgG9jWV0&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAS8AKf5xTkZ9ufPa7SBHpAl-N4QwiMkM2OnCTfGNHlug&oe=6709092E"}]}, "id": "534632578946828", "locale": "en_US", "screenshots": [{"file_name": "SS 1.png", "id": "214981191386453", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39036603_214981194719786_2204326445398023213_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=87VjNTS7Yk0Q7kNvgHFfZfy&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBDLW352EFYGXezcG4EGXT6RxLs9C1SgOYv8j5RNDKAAA&oe=6708FBAD"}, {"file_name": "SS 4.png", "id": "1454459558724650", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/86655530_1454459562057983_3389428944134145304_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=sPrZuPubs1MQ7kNvgH7xltI&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAkgg_Iv_t38DQFPilAkxtMUy-7IV5ekS83HZck3llYuw&oe=6708FAD2"}, {"file_name": "SS 5.png", "id": "194901913376228", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57575347_194901916709561_4369382863725734210_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=G9DtLkvYlWwQ7kNvgG4iQVw&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDE_N9ZDpPB3QYSKO0yKpNP4TNFTlg9tZNUiV5ocCenAA&oe=6708F936"}, {"file_name": "SS 6.png", "id": "2197528600634624", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/54770914_2197528603967957_7988230609053349225_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=os6Pd-2I4_YQ7kNvgHzXyzO&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDUH1bsFZVOftgcCC-_8RmEW2QQtX69cy933oijXqHSVg&oe=67091274"}, {"file_name": "SS 3.png", "id": "246141424576074", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/43931327_246141427909407_6276687811146681097_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=V8P0bZZ4t4MQ7kNvgEHesVo&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCZtLDp7sx1SfzVz2_FjVthgcos0ivnrEkCc48z0awV9A&oe=67091772"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Poster - Cover.png", "id": "1497330271070248", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982723_1497330274403581_1010539024953878920_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=hq59HTX6y_gQ7kNvgGRQr-U&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD2gMfFNZtf3Dq8MnoyWIdCWTLQzhc3HrTlHMk9rQPYhA&oe=670928D3"}, "display_name": "If You Are Not Dumb", "keywords": ["mr", "mixed", "reality", "puzzling", "places"], "long_description": "What if a puzzle looks simple BUT you end up feeling dumb!!\n\nIf You Are Not Dumb is a funny and quirky puzzle game.\n\nA game gives you situation based puzzles. A few objects to interact with and One instruction to follow!\n\nEach puzzle has its own logic.\n\nSituations are like -\n- Hide from the eyes, but eyes are everywhere\n- Extinguish fire when there is not water around you\n- Type BOX but without any keyboard!\n\nand many more!!\n\nA game also supports mixed reality! \n\nGive it a try! You will love the puzzles.. or at least you will realise that you are dumb (:\n\nTUK", "short_description": "What if a puzzle looks simple BUT you end up feeling dumb!!\n\nIf You Are Not Dumb is a funny and quirky puzzle game.\n\nA game gives you situation based puzzles. A few objects to interact with and One instruction to follow!\n\nEach puzzle has its own logic.\n\nSituations are like -\n- Hide from the eyes, but eyes are everywhere\n- Extinguish fire when there is not water around you\n- Type BOX but without any keyboard!\nand many more!!\n\nGive it a try! \nTUK"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://docs.google.com/document/d/1splZFw2pxh7oXEIZ2IEvGiGT4-rrTjDIGOP53sAiOiA/edit?usp=sharing", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Kishor Berde", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://www.kishorberde.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTA